The paper proposes a method for activity recognition using a single sensor, which involves representation learning and feature mapping. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses user comfort, privacy, and battery preservation, which are related to Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories. The paper also mentions using sensor data for computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE), which are also likely sub-categories.
